Who you really looking for?

217
00:24:43,275 --> 00:24:46,611
A pro. Calls himself "The Jackal. "

218
00:24:48,280 --> 00:24:50,115
That fellow.

219
00:24:51,575 --> 00:24:53,201
The mystery man.

220
00:24:54,119 --> 00:24:57,247
We think she may be able
to help us find him.

221
00:24:57,372 --> 00:24:59,624
If so, we'll arrange a pardon for her...

222
00:24:59,708 --> 00:25:02,127
...signed by the President of the US.

223
00:25:02,210 --> 00:25:05,922
And guarantee no extradition. We'd also
guarantee the Spanish government...

224
00:25:06,006 --> 00:25:09,801
...will never know her whereabouts.
- They don't know now, do they?

225
00:25:10,302 --> 00:25:12,012
And neither do you.

226
00:25:12,095 --> 00:25:14,014
Let's keep it that way.

227
00:25:22,647 --> 00:25:25,484
Would it matter that you might be
saving a human life?

228
00:25:25,567 --> 00:25:29,070
